altername_name: Los Lunnis: En Busca del Libro Magico
name: Los Lunnis: En Busca del Libro Magico
overview: The magic book of the witch Libina has disappeared. Follow Lucho in this fantastic adventure and play with all the famous characters from the TV series. Explore the wonderful world of Luna Lunera and enjoy with each and every one of your favorite characters, to the rhythm of the music of Los Lunnis.
